1
00:00:18,980 --> 00:00:24,420
♪It's a sordid story that you've made♪

2
00:00:26,700 --> 00:00:32,700
♪Up to fill my mind with doubts and pain♪

3
00:00:34,780 --> 00:00:40,220
♪Blood I shed, and tears I wept,
are you satisfied?♪

4
00:00:40,220 --> 00:00:42,540
♪Enjoying what's mine♪

5
00:00:42,540 --> 00:00:49,500
♪Have you found a way
to bury guilt and shame♪

6
00:00:50,540 --> 00:00:55,020
♪I'm coming back to life♪

7
00:00:55,020 --> 00:00:58,700
♪Through the seven gates of death♪

8
00:00:58,700 --> 00:01:02,820
♪I'm coming back survived♪

9
00:01:02,820 --> 00:01:06,580
♪Feeling great to see you fall♪

10
00:01:06,580 --> 00:01:10,820
♪I'm taking back what's mine♪

11
00:01:10,820 --> 00:01:15,340
♪Bringing horror to the battlefield♪

12
00:01:15,340 --> 00:01:19,060
♪Lay it to waste♪

13
00:01:19,060 --> 00:01:22,940
♪Til the day my kingdom is reclaimed♪

14
00:01:38,260 --> 00:01:42,540
=Her Blaze=

15
00:01:43,150 --> 00:01:45,962
=Episode 4=

16
00:01:51,087 --> 00:01:51,887
That's so cruel.

17
00:01:56,807 --> 00:01:57,607
Tian Tian.

18
00:01:58,162 --> 00:01:58,762
Look at them.

19
00:01:58,762 --> 00:02:00,242
Isn't it cruel?

20
00:02:03,607 --> 00:02:04,406
Mr. Huang,

21
00:02:05,087 --> 00:02:06,646
if there's nothing else,

22
00:02:07,006 --> 00:02:08,006
I'll make a move first.

23
00:02:10,486 --> 00:02:11,847
Since you're already here,

24
00:02:12,327 --> 00:02:12,966
that means

25
00:02:12,966 --> 00:02:15,447
you've accepted the deal, right?

26
00:02:17,206 --> 00:02:18,847
What deal?

27
00:02:27,007 --> 00:02:28,926
A deal for your future.

28
00:02:31,806 --> 00:02:32,847
What are you doing?

29
00:02:35,127 --> 00:02:35,926
Stop running!

30
00:02:36,167 --> 00:02:36,966
Stop running!

31
00:02:41,366 --> 00:02:42,926
Here I come!

32
00:02:57,926 --> 00:02:58,727
Tian Tian.

33
00:03:00,047 --> 00:03:01,567
You thought joining Lysen Group

34
00:03:01,567 --> 00:03:03,820
as an intern was the start of your life
in this industry.

35
00:03:04,500 --> 00:03:06,280
But the start of your life
in this industry

36
00:03:06,526 --> 00:03:08,486
begins with doing
an "internship" under me.

37
00:03:08,812 --> 00:03:10,425
(110)

38
00:03:10,475 --> 00:03:11,212
(Emergency Services)

39
00:03:12,720 --> 00:03:14,047
It's pointless to call the cops.

40
00:03:14,486 --> 00:03:15,887
You came here of your own accord.

41
00:03:18,650 --> 00:03:19,200
(Emergency Services)

42
00:03:19,262 --> 00:03:19,825
(Calls)

43
00:03:27,887 --> 00:03:29,206
You're a young girl.

44
00:03:29,275 --> 00:03:29,862
(Bai Liangliang, Miss Bai)

45
00:03:29,887 --> 00:03:31,150
You don't have any resources at all.

46
00:03:31,167 --> 00:03:33,167
Miss Bai, please pick up the phone.

47
00:03:33,167 --> 00:03:34,086
Please.

48
00:03:43,686 --> 00:03:45,167
I truly hope

49
00:03:45,167 --> 00:03:47,362
that I can become a friend
who understands you well.

50
00:03:54,327 --> 00:03:55,646
Miss Bai, please pick up.

51
00:03:55,806 --> 00:03:56,607
Please.

52
00:04:00,125 --> 00:04:01,350
(Tian Tian)

53
00:04:06,248 --> 00:04:07,047
Hello?

54
00:04:07,150 --> 00:04:07,950
Miss Bai!

55
00:04:08,486 --> 00:04:09,246
Miss Bai,

56
00:04:09,246 --> 00:04:10,966
can you please come and save me?

57
00:04:11,646 --> 00:04:12,926
Mr. Huang is drunk!

58
00:04:12,926 --> 00:04:13,766
He's going wild out there!

59
00:04:13,766 --> 00:04:15,007
He wouldn't let me leave!

60
00:04:15,327 --> 00:04:16,767
Please come and rescue me!

61
00:04:16,767 --> 00:04:17,566
So?

62
00:04:17,886 --> 00:04:19,647
Why did you choose to go, then?

63
00:04:20,246 --> 00:04:21,767
You were the one who chose

64
00:04:21,767 --> 00:04:23,326
to enter the room, right?

65
00:04:23,326 --> 00:04:24,047
That's not true!

66
00:04:24,047 --> 00:04:25,407
Mr. Liu Yang

67
00:04:25,407 --> 00:04:27,566
told me to come here to discuss
an in-depth cooperation with Mr. Huang!

68
00:04:27,566 --> 00:04:28,990
I didn't come here of my own accord!

69
00:04:29,366 --> 00:04:31,326
Even so, you made the choice yourself.

70
00:04:35,727 --> 00:04:36,767
As an adult,

71
00:04:36,967 --> 00:04:39,126
unspoken understanding
is a form of wisdom.

72
00:04:39,647 --> 00:04:41,446
If you wish to call the cops now,

73
00:04:42,050 --> 00:04:43,287
I'll support your decision too.

74
00:04:43,686 --> 00:04:44,806
But you need to know this.

75
00:04:45,126 --> 00:04:46,647
Both Mr. Huang and Lysen Group

76
00:04:47,126 --> 00:04:47,967
are more important

77
00:04:47,967 --> 00:04:50,686
than you, a flawed victim
that's not important at all.

78
00:04:55,806 --> 00:04:56,607
Tian Tian.

79
00:04:57,287 --> 00:04:58,727
Since you're already there,

80
00:04:58,900 --> 00:05:00,780
why don't you make things
easier for everyone?

81
00:05:00,900 --> 00:05:02,847
It's very difficult for you
to ascend the ranks

82
00:05:03,527 --> 00:05:04,847
by yourself.

83
00:05:06,047 --> 00:05:08,387
And, Mr. Huang is a friend of Mr. Jiang.

84
00:05:08,847 --> 00:05:09,607
At this moment,

85
00:05:09,607 --> 00:05:11,326
if you make Mr. Huang upset,

86
00:05:11,527 --> 00:05:14,207
Mr. Jiang will be upset as well.

87
00:05:16,207 --> 00:05:17,006
Hello?

88
00:05:18,047 --> 00:05:18,847
Miss Bai?

89
00:05:22,486 --> 00:05:23,287
Tian Tian?

90
00:05:27,686 --> 00:05:28,486
Tian Tian.

91
00:05:31,006 --> 00:05:32,087
Have you made up your mind?

92
00:05:52,475 --> 00:05:55,662
(Close, Open)

93
00:06:10,886 --> 00:06:11,806
Mr. Huang.

94
00:06:14,326 --> 00:06:16,486
You're almost the same age as my father.

95
00:06:19,006 --> 00:06:20,326
Can you please let me go?

96
00:06:21,886 --> 00:06:23,047
I'm begging you here.

97
00:06:23,566 --> 00:06:24,806
I don't want to do this.

98
00:06:27,087 --> 00:06:28,246
Please.

99
00:06:33,926 --> 00:06:34,727
Good girl.

100
00:06:34,886 --> 00:06:35,686
Come here.

101
00:07:09,326 --> 00:07:10,886
You said I could call you

102
00:07:11,047 --> 00:07:12,446
for anything, right?

103
00:07:15,625 --> 00:07:18,887
(Baiying Business Investigation)

104
00:07:20,486 --> 00:07:22,886
I love it when you call me Mr. Huang.

105
00:07:24,087 --> 00:07:25,686
Call me that again.

106
00:07:38,207 --> 00:07:39,006
Help!

107
00:07:43,366 --> 00:07:44,167
Please save me!

108
00:07:44,847 --> 00:07:45,767
Who are you?

109
00:07:47,100 --> 00:07:49,180
The door is unlocked.
He's asking me for my identity.

110
00:07:49,220 --> 00:07:50,446
There's no need to answer him.

111
00:07:51,000 --> 00:07:52,886
Dr. Chen, just do
what you're supposed to do.

112
00:07:54,767 --> 00:07:55,926
Please save me!

113
00:08:07,320 --> 00:08:08,446
I'm going to call the cops!

114
00:08:08,446 --> 00:08:09,686
Suit yourself.

115
00:08:10,607 --> 00:08:11,767
I saw what you did

116
00:08:11,767 --> 00:08:12,727
to the girl just now.

117
00:08:13,250 --> 00:08:14,727
This is a reminder from someone else.

118
00:08:15,446 --> 00:08:17,926
You have to clean up a huge mess
after calling the cops.

119
00:08:19,126 --> 00:08:21,047
And, you're a public figure yourself.

120
00:08:31,366 --> 00:08:32,407
The press conference

121
00:08:32,566 --> 00:08:34,920
for our investment in Dada Wine Industry
is in ten minutes.

122
00:08:35,167 --> 00:08:36,086
No matter what,

123
00:08:36,206 --> 00:08:36,887
I'll definitely

124
00:08:36,887 --> 00:08:38,127
take this project on.

125
00:08:45,527 --> 00:08:46,300
This is the material

126
00:08:46,310 --> 00:08:48,620
related to Zhaohui Private Equity
that I've just received.

127
00:08:55,086 --> 00:08:55,887
Rao Yuci,

128
00:08:57,806 --> 00:08:59,262
I want to tell you about

129
00:09:00,487 --> 00:09:01,686
the way I do things once again.

130
00:09:01,900 --> 00:09:04,367
As long as the overall direction
of this project is sound,

131
00:09:05,287 --> 00:09:07,206
and it can help Lysen Group
to make a profit,

132
00:09:08,726 --> 00:09:09,966
I don't care if the people below

133
00:09:11,350 --> 00:09:12,407
make some money from this.

134
00:09:13,247 --> 00:09:14,367
You can do the same as well.

135
00:09:16,686 --> 00:09:19,127
How about the fake liquor
company financial report?

136
00:09:21,000 --> 00:09:22,846
Mr. Li has always been
keeping an eye on you.

137
00:09:23,287 --> 00:09:24,767
Once this landmine detonates,

138
00:09:24,900 --> 00:09:26,566
you'll be held accountable
by the company.

139
00:09:27,206 --> 00:09:28,726
And, your reputation

140
00:09:29,287 --> 00:09:30,007
in this industry

141
00:09:30,007 --> 00:09:31,527
will be utterly ruined.

142
00:09:43,806 --> 00:09:44,806
Mr. Jiang is here.

143
00:09:50,167 --> 00:09:51,966
Mr. Jiang.

144
00:09:51,966 --> 00:09:53,247
Mr. Jiang, look over here.

145
00:09:54,686 --> 00:09:55,367
Mr. Jiang.

146
00:09:55,367 --> 00:09:56,446
Mr. Jiang!

147
00:09:59,846 --> 00:10:01,606
Miss Gao, Mr. Jiang is almost here.

148
00:10:01,606 --> 00:10:02,527
Let's head downstairs.

149
00:10:02,527 --> 00:10:03,287
Miss Bai.

150
00:10:04,926 --> 00:10:06,047
Mr. Jiang

151
00:10:06,326 --> 00:10:07,647
instructed me to tell you

152
00:10:08,000 --> 00:10:09,790
that you don't need
to go downstairs anymore.

153
00:10:10,846 --> 00:10:11,647
What does that mean?

154
00:10:12,367 --> 00:10:14,007
Mr. Jiang instructed me to tell you

155
00:10:14,127 --> 00:10:15,380
that there's a chance of plans.

156
00:10:15,647 --> 00:10:18,206
You can watch the live broadcast
on the TV later.

157
00:10:27,367 --> 00:10:28,167
Hello, everyone.

158
00:10:28,887 --> 00:10:30,086
This press conference

159
00:10:30,287 --> 00:10:32,806
is related to Lysen Group
and Dada Wine Industry.

160
00:10:33,527 --> 00:10:36,527
After thorough consideration
by all parties,

161
00:10:36,887 --> 00:10:38,047
our final decision

162
00:10:40,800 --> 00:10:42,900
is to suspend our investment
in Dada Wine Industry.

163
00:10:45,487 --> 00:10:47,007
And, we shall reassess the projects

164
00:10:47,446 --> 00:10:48,647
of Dada Wine Industry.

165
00:10:49,127 --> 00:10:49,846
Mr. Jiang,

166
00:10:49,846 --> 00:10:51,206
this is quite the sudden decision.

167
00:10:51,206 --> 00:10:52,430
I'm sure something happened, right?

168
00:10:52,446 --> 00:10:53,410
I have just received

169
00:10:53,420 --> 00:10:55,086
the analysis report
on Dada Wine Industry

170
00:10:55,086 --> 00:10:56,950
from our investment department's
professional analysts.

171
00:10:56,966 --> 00:10:58,247
According to our understanding,

172
00:10:58,250 --> 00:11:00,887
Dada Wine Industry lacks the foundational
capabilities in all aspects

173
00:11:00,887 --> 00:11:02,527
to develop financial derivatives.

174
00:11:02,647 --> 00:11:03,806
Traditional liquor businesses

175
00:11:03,806 --> 00:11:05,047
like Dada Wine Industry have

176
00:11:05,050 --> 00:11:06,980
relatively straightforward
business operations.

177
00:11:07,420 --> 00:11:08,966
It's very easy for them
to become a target

178
00:11:08,966 --> 00:11:10,846
for exploitation by capital players.

179
00:11:11,566 --> 00:11:12,926
Since you don't intend to invest in

180
00:11:12,926 --> 00:11:13,966
Dada Wine Industry,

181
00:11:13,966 --> 00:11:15,846
what made you choose
to announce the decision here?

182
00:11:15,846 --> 00:11:16,806
Everyone knows

183
00:11:17,367 --> 00:11:19,647
Dada Wine Industry
came from my hometown.

184
00:11:20,247 --> 00:11:21,086
I cannot tolerate

185
00:11:21,086 --> 00:11:23,580
people using a project in my hometown
as a tool to raise funds!

186
00:11:24,047 --> 00:11:24,887
(Mr. Jiang,)

187
00:11:25,566 --> 00:11:27,086
(a crisis can also be an opportunity.)

188
00:11:27,887 --> 00:11:28,647
(You can leverage)

189
00:11:28,647 --> 00:11:30,527
(this press conference)

190
00:11:30,800 --> 00:11:32,926
(to prominently showcase
your investment philosophy.)

191
00:11:32,926 --> 00:11:35,606
I'll protect the hard-earned money
of every investor!

192
00:11:35,647 --> 00:11:38,007
When you're delivering such messages
in this spotlight,

193
00:11:38,500 --> 00:11:40,460
not only are you
a representative of Lysen Group,

194
00:11:41,127 --> 00:11:42,980
but you're also
the role model of the industry.

195
00:11:43,966 --> 00:11:45,247
Your personal image

196
00:11:45,726 --> 00:11:47,287
will become the brand of Lysen Group.

197
00:11:47,806 --> 00:11:49,086
With such a reputation,

198
00:11:49,686 --> 00:11:51,887
Mr. Li has no reason to kick you out.

199
00:11:58,487 --> 00:11:59,287
Here,

200
00:11:59,726 --> 00:12:01,086
I hope everyone will believe

201
00:12:01,527 --> 00:12:02,606
that I'll utilize the power

202
00:12:02,606 --> 00:12:03,966
of both Lysen Group and I

203
00:12:03,966 --> 00:12:04,606
to make

204
00:12:04,606 --> 00:12:05,806
this market healthier.

205
00:12:05,966 --> 00:12:07,247
It's because I, Jiang Dongchao,

206
00:12:07,566 --> 00:12:08,686
is responsible for

207
00:12:08,686 --> 00:12:10,127
all strategic decisions

208
00:12:12,007 --> 00:12:12,806
at Lysen Group.

209
00:12:23,326 --> 00:12:24,127
Mr. Jiang.

210
00:12:25,600 --> 00:12:26,966
Mr. Jiang, I'll make a move first.

211
00:12:32,007 --> 00:12:33,686
I'm the head of Investment Dept 1.

212
00:12:33,806 --> 00:12:34,686
Why didn't you tell me

213
00:12:34,686 --> 00:12:35,806
about your true thoughts?

214
00:12:35,810 --> 00:12:37,167
You tried to enter the market early

215
00:12:37,167 --> 00:12:38,690
and make a profit
through Zhaohui Private Equity.

216
00:12:38,846 --> 00:12:39,966
I don't care about that.

217
00:12:40,120 --> 00:12:41,926
But you harbored thoughts
you shouldn't have.

218
00:12:42,367 --> 00:12:44,007
Do you think I have no idea

219
00:12:44,846 --> 00:12:46,167
about your true motives?

220
00:12:49,846 --> 00:12:50,966
Don't you trust me?

221
00:12:51,247 --> 00:12:52,047
Bai Liangliang.

222
00:12:52,767 --> 00:12:53,846
You kept your options open

223
00:12:53,846 --> 00:12:54,806
and went with the flow.

224
00:12:55,206 --> 00:12:56,247
That's fine and all.

225
00:12:57,647 --> 00:12:58,767
But do you think

226
00:12:58,887 --> 00:13:00,606
you're more intelligent
than other people?

227
00:13:00,610 --> 00:13:02,806
You thought you understood everything,
could make every plan,

228
00:13:02,806 --> 00:13:04,190
and manipulate everyone around you.

229
00:13:04,887 --> 00:13:06,367
But everyone is just as intelligent.

230
00:13:07,787 --> 00:13:09,400
Just like your good friend, Rao Yuci.

231
00:13:11,060 --> 00:13:12,600
She's much more intelligent than you.

232
00:13:29,806 --> 00:13:31,086
Come and take a look.

233
00:13:41,362 --> 00:13:45,150
(Fruit Bowl)

234
00:13:46,167 --> 00:13:46,966
Thanks.

235
00:13:53,206 --> 00:13:54,290
You should have something.

236
00:14:07,407 --> 00:14:08,247
Thank you.

237
00:14:11,086 --> 00:14:11,887
Thank you.

238
00:14:12,926 --> 00:14:15,007
Thank you for asking Dr. Chen
to rescue me.

239
00:14:17,887 --> 00:14:20,167
I didn't even have
the courage to resist.

240
00:14:22,767 --> 00:14:24,007
I brought this upon myself.

241
00:14:36,420 --> 00:14:37,726
I was just like you in the past.

242
00:14:40,167 --> 00:14:41,767
I wanted someone else to save me too.

243
00:14:45,926 --> 00:14:47,527
Get the keys! Someone!

244
00:14:47,726 --> 00:14:48,527
Open the door!

245
00:14:49,647 --> 00:14:50,446
Open the door!

246
00:14:51,407 --> 00:14:52,487
Mom, I'm Yuci.

247
00:14:53,287 --> 00:14:54,086
You...

248
00:14:54,446 --> 00:14:56,926
Can you please come and see me alone?

249
00:14:58,566 --> 00:14:59,527
Mom, I'm begging you!

250
00:14:59,527 --> 00:15:01,206
Please come and see me alone!

251
00:15:02,086 --> 00:15:03,606
But in the end, you'll realize

252
00:15:06,420 --> 00:15:08,490
that you're the only person
capable of saving yourself.

253
00:15:17,740 --> 00:15:19,367
Tian Tian, regarding
the encounter today,

254
00:15:22,086 --> 00:15:23,407
you oversimplified it.

255
00:15:23,926 --> 00:15:26,287
I never expected this to happen.

256
00:15:26,527 --> 00:15:27,527
Facing Bai Liangliang's

257
00:15:27,527 --> 00:15:28,767
and Liu Yang's invitation,

258
00:15:29,287 --> 00:15:30,127
I'm sure you detected

259
00:15:30,127 --> 00:15:31,086
a sense of danger.

260
00:15:32,200 --> 00:15:34,247
Even so, you thought it would
turn out for the best.

261
00:15:34,407 --> 00:15:35,566
I... I didn't know

262
00:15:35,566 --> 00:15:37,326
- that it would end up like this.
- Yes.

263
00:15:37,326 --> 00:15:38,287
You'll think

264
00:15:38,926 --> 00:15:39,686
that you might be

265
00:15:39,686 --> 00:15:41,047
the luckiest person out there.

266
00:15:42,637 --> 00:15:43,926
But I'm different from you.

267
00:15:43,926 --> 00:15:45,566
I'm not as capable as you.

268
00:15:45,806 --> 00:15:47,487
I had no choice
but to let them trample upon me.

269
00:15:47,487 --> 00:15:48,167
If so,

270
00:15:48,167 --> 00:15:49,127
become stronger.

271
00:15:49,686 --> 00:15:51,127
Make yourself strong.

272
00:15:52,926 --> 00:15:54,007
But the prerequisite is

273
00:15:54,726 --> 00:15:55,966
that you need to trust yourself.

274
00:15:56,487 --> 00:15:58,527
You need to be brave
and learn how to retaliate.

275
00:15:58,660 --> 00:16:01,167
Only then will you be able
to defeat those who break the rules,

276
00:16:01,647 --> 00:16:02,966
and those who are unkind.

277
00:16:03,500 --> 00:16:05,367
Let them see
the consequences of their actions.

278
00:16:08,500 --> 00:16:09,647
It's because they don't know

279
00:16:09,647 --> 00:16:10,726
the extent of honest people.

280
00:16:11,700 --> 00:16:14,206
They think that honest people
have no roles in any stories.

281
00:16:15,326 --> 00:16:16,767
But we need to tell them

282
00:16:18,647 --> 00:16:19,487
that we'll never be

283
00:16:19,487 --> 00:16:20,926
the oriole trapped in a cage.

284
00:16:26,647 --> 00:16:28,407
Are you even in that story, Rao Yuci?

285
00:16:29,167 --> 00:16:30,566
In the story with the oriole,

286
00:16:31,806 --> 00:16:33,407
what role do you play?

287
00:16:39,726 --> 00:16:40,527
Mom,

288
00:16:40,767 --> 00:16:42,966
is the oriole the strongest?

289
00:16:46,206 --> 00:16:47,887
Who's the strongest, then?

290
00:16:48,647 --> 00:16:50,487
Let me tell you. Look here.

291
00:16:50,846 --> 00:16:52,846
The mantis wants to hunt the cicada,

292
00:16:53,326 --> 00:16:54,606
but it doesn't know

293
00:16:54,606 --> 00:16:57,127
that the oriole is behind it
and that it's going to eat it.

294
00:16:57,926 --> 00:16:59,047
But the oriole doesn't know

295
00:16:59,047 --> 00:17:00,686
that there's a boy

296
00:17:00,686 --> 00:17:01,887
at the foot of the tree,

297
00:17:02,167 --> 00:17:04,007
trying to shoot it down.

298
00:17:04,247 --> 00:17:05,687
But this boy

299
00:17:05,687 --> 00:17:07,047
doesn't know

300
00:17:07,047 --> 00:17:07,687
that

301
00:17:07,687 --> 00:17:09,687
there's a deep water puddle behind him.

302
00:17:09,727 --> 00:17:10,846
It's very dangerous.

303
00:17:11,406 --> 00:17:12,247
Therefore,

304
00:17:12,566 --> 00:17:13,366
you see,

305
00:17:13,406 --> 00:17:14,207
in this story,

306
00:17:14,287 --> 00:17:15,967
no one is the strongest.

307
00:17:17,967 --> 00:17:18,646
So Yuci,

308
00:17:18,646 --> 00:17:19,967
you must remember this.

309
00:17:20,527 --> 00:17:21,806
You must be kind.

310
00:17:22,447 --> 00:17:23,527
Only kindness

311
00:17:23,527 --> 00:17:24,727
will never be exposed.

312
00:17:25,366 --> 00:17:26,566
Only by being kind

313
00:17:26,886 --> 00:17:28,767
will you not harm anyone else.

314
00:17:28,927 --> 00:17:29,967
That's the only way

315
00:17:30,207 --> 00:17:31,487
you won't become

316
00:17:31,487 --> 00:17:33,207
any of the characters in the story.

317
00:17:33,406 --> 00:17:34,366
Remember it, okay?

318
00:17:34,527 --> 00:17:35,846
Yes, Mom.

319
00:17:40,247 --> 00:17:41,047
Miss Meng.

320
00:17:41,287 --> 00:17:42,287
Take off your high heels.

321
00:17:42,287 --> 00:17:43,527
This isn't the right occasion for it.

322
00:17:43,527 --> 00:17:44,406
We need to run, huh?

323
00:17:44,527 --> 00:17:45,326
Yeah.

324
00:17:51,606 --> 00:17:52,406
Thank you.

325
00:17:53,337 --> 00:17:57,312
(Investment Dept 1)

326
00:18:01,447 --> 00:18:03,126
Miss Bai, we're in trouble.

327
00:18:03,126 --> 00:18:03,606
Mr. Yu

328
00:18:03,606 --> 00:18:04,927
brought Investment Dept 3 here.

329
00:18:04,927 --> 00:18:06,207
He said Mr. Jiang requested

330
00:18:06,207 --> 00:18:08,110
a review of all project details
managed by our department.

331
00:18:08,126 --> 00:18:09,487
They're currently
reviewing the materials

332
00:18:09,487 --> 00:18:10,790
and preparing to take them away.

333
00:18:24,886 --> 00:18:25,687
Rao Yuci!

334
00:18:30,326 --> 00:18:31,126
What's the matter?

335
00:18:31,920 --> 00:18:33,990
Miss Bai, do you wish
to speak with me in private?

336
00:18:34,680 --> 00:18:35,606
You're something else.

337
00:18:54,207 --> 00:18:55,846
You're a crafty wretch, aren't you?

338
00:18:55,860 --> 00:18:56,927
What exactly are you up to?

339
00:18:56,927 --> 00:18:58,366
What has that got to do with you?

340
00:18:59,566 --> 00:19:00,846
Besides, dealing with you

341
00:19:01,646 --> 00:19:02,846
is no big deal for me.

342
00:19:03,620 --> 00:19:06,287
Do you think you've won just because
you've won the support of Mr. Jiang?

343
00:19:11,086 --> 00:19:14,406
I don't need the support of anyone
to win against you.

344
00:19:16,487 --> 00:19:18,287
I really don't understand.

345
00:19:18,300 --> 00:19:20,447
Where does a lunatic like you
get the nerve to do this?

346
00:19:20,447 --> 00:19:21,687
Speak for yourself.

347
00:19:23,967 --> 00:19:24,806
You're a useless fool

348
00:19:24,806 --> 00:19:26,207
who's worse than a lunatic like me.

349
00:19:29,437 --> 00:19:31,112
Rao Yuci, listen up.

350
00:19:31,646 --> 00:19:33,806
Although you were released
from the treatment center,

351
00:19:33,846 --> 00:19:35,406
I can still send you back!

352
00:19:39,086 --> 00:19:40,806
But I've changed
in the past three years.

353
00:19:40,886 --> 00:19:42,247
No matter how much you changed,

354
00:19:42,447 --> 00:19:43,086
you're still

355
00:19:43,086 --> 00:19:45,086
a lunatic who stabbed her own mother.

356
00:19:48,527 --> 00:19:49,326
That's right.

357
00:19:50,366 --> 00:19:51,366
You know the best

358
00:19:51,366 --> 00:19:52,527
about our family affairs.

359
00:19:53,447 --> 00:19:54,126
If so,

360
00:19:54,126 --> 00:19:55,927
you should fear
for your life after this.

361
00:19:57,047 --> 00:20:00,086
You'll never know
what a lunatic is thinking about

362
00:20:01,247 --> 00:20:02,606
and trying to do, you know?

363
00:20:11,166 --> 00:20:11,806
Are they okay?

364
00:20:11,806 --> 00:20:13,287
Let's go and take a look.

365
00:20:13,406 --> 00:20:14,207
Who is it?

366
00:20:14,247 --> 00:20:16,287
Make way.

367
00:20:19,487 --> 00:20:20,287
Rao Yuci?

368
00:20:20,967 --> 00:20:21,767
Where's the key?

369
00:20:21,767 --> 00:20:22,566
I...

370
00:20:22,566 --> 00:20:23,326
Get out of the way.

371
00:20:23,487 --> 00:20:24,287
Get out of the way!

372
00:20:24,287 --> 00:20:25,207
Make way.

373
00:20:28,527 --> 00:20:29,326
What's the matter?

374
00:20:31,800 --> 00:20:32,900
What happened to your hand?

375
00:20:34,566 --> 00:20:36,047
I hurt myself by accident.

376
00:20:36,646 --> 00:20:38,007
You guys should check on Miss Bai.

377
00:20:38,040 --> 00:20:39,287
I think she was quite startled.

378
00:20:40,326 --> 00:20:41,126
Are you okay?

379
00:20:55,326 --> 00:20:56,326
I thought professionals

380
00:20:56,326 --> 00:20:57,207
like you all

381
00:20:59,447 --> 00:21:00,806
are not adept at schemes.

382
00:21:03,927 --> 00:21:05,527
It depends on who the boss is

383
00:21:05,886 --> 00:21:06,687
and

384
00:21:07,767 --> 00:21:08,967
who's the target.

385
00:21:11,606 --> 00:21:12,406
Rao Yuci?

386
00:21:14,200 --> 00:21:17,937
♪Through the seven gates of death♪

387
00:21:18,007 --> 00:21:19,007
Bai Liangliang.

388
00:21:19,646 --> 00:21:20,646
The game

389
00:21:20,646 --> 00:21:22,086
is just starting.

390
00:21:22,086 --> 00:21:25,225
♪Feeling great to see you fall♪

391
00:21:25,500 --> 00:21:30,012
♪I'm taking back what's mine♪

392
00:21:30,362 --> 00:21:33,662
♪Bringing horror to the battlefield♪

393
00:21:33,862 --> 00:21:37,887
♪Lay it to waste♪

394
00:21:38,037 --> 00:21:43,575
♪Til the day my kingdom is reclaimed♪

395
00:21:54,086 --> 00:21:54,886
Rao Yuci?

396
00:21:59,886 --> 00:22:01,047
Rao Yuci, this is Chen Mo.

397
00:22:03,207 --> 00:22:04,007
Young man.

398
00:22:05,806 --> 00:22:06,886
Who are you looking for?

399
00:22:07,400 --> 00:22:09,400
I'm looking for the girl
who's been living here.

400
00:22:09,487 --> 00:22:10,447
Where did she go?

401
00:22:10,927 --> 00:22:11,967
She left with her luggage

402
00:22:11,967 --> 00:22:13,727
early in the morning.

403
00:22:14,287 --> 00:22:15,406
With her luggage?

404
00:22:15,447 --> 00:22:18,366
Yeah. She said she was
going on a distant trip.

405
00:22:18,487 --> 00:22:20,086
Stop knocking on her door.

406
00:22:20,166 --> 00:22:21,447
It's very irritating.

407
00:22:46,550 --> 00:22:48,650
(Linwei Alley)

408
00:22:55,846 --> 00:22:57,527
He had a severe stroke two years ago.

409
00:22:57,767 --> 00:22:59,487
He couldn't do
without people around him.

410
00:23:00,646 --> 00:23:02,606
Mr. Xu's pension alone

411
00:23:03,086 --> 00:23:04,287
isn't enough to sustain

412
00:23:04,287 --> 00:23:05,886
his treatment fees.

413
00:23:08,287 --> 00:23:09,247
I had no choice

414
00:23:09,967 --> 00:23:11,287
but to seek help online.

415
00:23:12,247 --> 00:23:13,086
Don't worry.

416
00:23:13,606 --> 00:23:15,207
I'm not here to ask you for money.

417
00:23:20,047 --> 00:23:21,447
I'll definitely repay my debt.

418
00:23:30,487 --> 00:23:31,687
Who's living in the room

419
00:23:31,687 --> 00:23:32,646
with the closed door?

420
00:23:36,927 --> 00:23:37,727
It's my daughter.

421
00:23:39,727 --> 00:23:40,967
Is she living with you?

422
00:23:45,800 --> 00:23:47,220
I'm not comfortable discussing that.

423
00:23:49,487 --> 00:23:50,927
Why don't you rent the room to me?

424
00:23:56,646 --> 00:23:57,727
You don't lack money.

425
00:23:58,767 --> 00:24:00,086
Why are you trying to live here?

426
00:24:01,280 --> 00:24:02,990
I'm not comfortable
discussing that either.

427
00:24:03,500 --> 00:24:05,326
You said you wanted
to repay your debt, right?

428
00:24:06,047 --> 00:24:07,406
Treat this as a way

429
00:24:08,126 --> 00:24:09,247
to repay your debt, then.

430
00:24:13,887 --> 00:24:16,137
(Award Certificate, Bai Liangliang)

431
00:24:16,550 --> 00:24:19,300
(Certificate of Honor)

432
00:24:23,086 --> 00:24:24,767
I've already cleaned up
the room for you.

433
00:24:25,527 --> 00:24:26,366
I've also given you

434
00:24:26,366 --> 00:24:27,406
new blankets and sheets.

435
00:24:27,967 --> 00:24:29,447
You can stay here with peace of mind.

436
00:24:30,007 --> 00:24:31,806
I'll pay my rent after this.

437
00:24:32,527 --> 00:24:33,326
No need for that.

438
00:24:33,727 --> 00:24:35,287
You've helped us out so much.

439
00:24:35,566 --> 00:24:37,487
We can't afford to charge you any rent.

440
00:24:37,967 --> 00:24:39,687
I've kept all your

441
00:24:40,166 --> 00:24:41,366
money transfer receipts too.

442
00:24:41,687 --> 00:24:43,086
I'll definitely repay my debt

443
00:24:43,086 --> 00:24:44,287
once I save enough money.

444
00:24:45,086 --> 00:24:46,806
Just take this place as your home.

445
00:24:46,850 --> 00:24:48,646
You can stay here
for as long as you want.

446
00:24:50,000 --> 00:24:51,126
You can unpack your things first.

447
00:24:51,126 --> 00:24:52,287
Join us for lunch later.

448
00:25:09,846 --> 00:25:10,646
Mr. Jiang,

449
00:25:10,927 --> 00:25:11,806
here's your document.

450
00:25:11,967 --> 00:25:12,767
Thank you.

451
00:25:13,927 --> 00:25:14,727
Please.

452
00:25:25,126 --> 00:25:25,927
Is this osmanthus?

453
00:25:26,000 --> 00:25:27,287
But this isn't the season for it.

454
00:25:27,646 --> 00:25:29,606
Miss Bai prepared this
especially for you.

455
00:25:32,566 --> 00:25:35,086
One time, I mentioned by accident
that you were coughing.

456
00:25:35,126 --> 00:25:36,290
And, you didn't like medicine.

457
00:25:36,400 --> 00:25:38,287
Miss Bai said osmanthus tea
has a gentle flavor

458
00:25:38,287 --> 00:25:39,110
and a pleasant taste.

459
00:25:39,300 --> 00:25:40,780
And, it can dissolve phlegm as well.

460
00:25:40,860 --> 00:25:41,967
That's why she procured some

461
00:25:41,967 --> 00:25:44,527
fresh osmanthus so that I could make
osmanthus tea for you.

462
00:25:46,460 --> 00:25:47,727
She's outside my office, right?

463
00:25:49,380 --> 00:25:51,080
She was already here
early in the morning.

464
00:25:53,527 --> 00:25:54,487
Tell her to come in.

465
00:25:54,687 --> 00:25:55,487
Okay.

466
00:26:07,487 --> 00:26:08,326
Mr. Jiang.

467
00:26:11,100 --> 00:26:13,166
I've heard about what happened
in Investment Dept 1.

468
00:26:14,025 --> 00:26:17,287
Miss Bai, don't you think
you were too reckless?

469
00:26:18,886 --> 00:26:19,687
Mr. Jiang,

470
00:26:20,606 --> 00:26:22,070
I've been following in your footsteps

471
00:26:22,086 --> 00:26:23,606
right after I joined Lysen Group.

472
00:26:24,287 --> 00:26:26,126
I've done so many things
for Lysen Group.

473
00:26:26,207 --> 00:26:27,326
I'm sure you understand

474
00:26:27,886 --> 00:26:29,047
that everything I did,

475
00:26:29,166 --> 00:26:30,166
I did it for your sake

476
00:26:30,406 --> 00:26:31,606
and Lysen Group's sake.

477
00:26:32,300 --> 00:26:33,927
Therefore, I have to give you a reminder.

478
00:26:34,326 --> 00:26:35,846
Rao Yuci is a huge threat

479
00:26:36,007 --> 00:26:37,047
to Lysen Group.

480
00:26:37,886 --> 00:26:39,207
Whether she's a threat or not,

481
00:26:40,007 --> 00:26:41,166
I'll judge that myself.

482
00:26:44,927 --> 00:26:46,487
Bai Liangliang, oh, Bai Liangliang,

483
00:26:47,000 --> 00:26:49,007
you resemble
the younger version of me too much.

484
00:26:51,020 --> 00:26:52,750
You lay your ambitions bare
for all to see.

485
00:26:53,927 --> 00:26:54,727
However,

486
00:26:57,126 --> 00:26:58,207
I wasn't as foolish as you

487
00:27:01,126 --> 00:27:02,247
when I was your age.

488
00:27:05,207 --> 00:27:06,886
Whether or not you did all those things

489
00:27:06,886 --> 00:27:08,160
were for the sake of Lysen Group,

490
00:27:08,247 --> 00:27:09,047
I'm sure

491
00:27:09,366 --> 00:27:10,806
we all know the best.

492
00:27:12,406 --> 00:27:13,727
Do you think I have no idea?

493
00:27:15,166 --> 00:27:16,406
Rao Yuci's appearance

494
00:27:18,086 --> 00:27:19,406
is a threat to you.

495
00:27:21,100 --> 00:27:22,126
That's why you fear her.

496
00:27:22,126 --> 00:27:22,687
I don't fear her!

497
00:27:22,687 --> 00:27:24,350
I don't care about the affairs
between you two.

498
00:27:24,366 --> 00:27:25,487
I don't want to know either.

499
00:27:27,126 --> 00:27:28,566
To both Lysen Group and me,

500
00:27:28,566 --> 00:27:29,366
Rao Yuci is useful.

501
00:27:29,600 --> 00:27:30,967
However, if you try to jeopardize

502
00:27:31,047 --> 00:27:32,606
my interest and Lysen Group's interest,

503
00:27:32,606 --> 00:27:33,750
I won't show you any mercy.

504
00:27:34,326 --> 00:27:35,366
That's my bottom line.

505
00:27:36,247 --> 00:27:37,047
So,

506
00:27:38,100 --> 00:27:39,220
don't try to test my limits.

507
00:27:40,566 --> 00:27:41,846
Don't count on your luck.

508
00:27:42,300 --> 00:27:44,406
And, don't be so foolish
that you'll try to make me

509
00:27:44,406 --> 00:27:45,480
choose between you and her.

510
00:27:48,646 --> 00:27:49,806
I'm sure you know the answer.

511
00:27:53,207 --> 00:27:54,126
I know.

512
00:27:57,326 --> 00:27:58,287
Speaking of choices,

513
00:27:59,326 --> 00:28:00,687
I'm curious about something.

514
00:28:01,360 --> 00:28:03,086
Miss Bai, will you
choose to side with me?

515
00:28:06,700 --> 00:28:08,287
Or will you choose to side with Mr. Li?

516
00:28:14,166 --> 00:28:15,287
When I was young,

517
00:28:15,487 --> 00:28:16,727
I recognized my position

518
00:28:17,180 --> 00:28:18,207
and chose the right path.

519
00:28:19,320 --> 00:28:20,687
It's the same for you right now.

520
00:28:21,880 --> 00:28:24,007
It's vital for you
to recognize your own position.

521
00:28:29,326 --> 00:28:30,126
Miss Gao,

522
00:28:30,606 --> 00:28:31,767
get me a cup of plain water.

523
00:28:32,126 --> 00:28:33,166
Alright, Mr. Jiang.

524
00:28:33,527 --> 00:28:34,326
Thanks.

525
00:28:38,047 --> 00:28:39,190
Thanks for the osmanthus tea.

526
00:28:44,287 --> 00:28:45,166
You may leave now.

527
00:28:46,767 --> 00:28:47,566
Yes, Mr. Jiang.

528
00:29:20,287 --> 00:29:21,326
Hello? Who is this?

529
00:29:22,487 --> 00:29:23,287
It's me.

530
00:29:47,086 --> 00:29:49,126
Hello. Are you Dr. Chen Mo?

531
00:29:49,447 --> 00:29:50,247
Hello.

532
00:29:50,806 --> 00:29:51,846
I'm Bai Liangliang.

533
00:29:51,886 --> 00:29:53,086
Nice to meet you.

534
00:29:53,126 --> 00:29:53,927
Likewise.

535
00:29:55,120 --> 00:29:55,967
I'm now in charge of

536
00:29:55,967 --> 00:29:57,646
(Chen Mo)
Rao Yuci's follow-up visit.

537
00:29:59,047 --> 00:30:00,860
But I couldn't
get in touch with her lately.

538
00:30:01,000 --> 00:30:02,900
I couldn't get in touch
with her parents either.

539
00:30:03,406 --> 00:30:04,846
You're her emergency contact.

540
00:30:05,287 --> 00:30:07,300
Do you know something
about her recent condition?

541
00:30:09,207 --> 00:30:10,326
As her attending physician,

542
00:30:10,566 --> 00:30:11,967
do you think she has recovered?

543
00:30:12,767 --> 00:30:13,967
Judging from her recovery,

544
00:30:13,967 --> 00:30:14,830
I think she's doing well.

545
00:30:14,846 --> 00:30:17,290
But she still needs the support
of her family members after this.

546
00:30:18,406 --> 00:30:20,126
What if that doesn't exist?

547
00:30:22,086 --> 00:30:25,166
As a friend, I should try to help her
get her emotions under control.

548
00:30:25,326 --> 00:30:26,566
After all, she has now returned

549
00:30:26,566 --> 00:30:27,927
to her normal work routine.

550
00:30:33,687 --> 00:30:35,487
Since you're this
concerned about Rao Yuci,

551
00:30:35,886 --> 00:30:36,967
why don't you do me a favor?

552
00:30:38,775 --> 00:30:50,475
(Saltwater Duck)

553
00:30:54,767 --> 00:30:55,566
Please go ahead.

554
00:30:57,166 --> 00:30:57,967
Okay.

555
00:31:03,625 --> 00:31:04,425
Okay, no problem.

556
00:31:21,275 --> 00:31:27,062
(To my best friend, Liangliang.
From Rao Yuci)

557
00:31:29,047 --> 00:31:29,846
Liangliang,

558
00:31:30,606 --> 00:31:31,810
I've prepared a gift for you

559
00:31:31,820 --> 00:31:33,727
to celebrate your
successful thesis defense.

560
00:31:33,767 --> 00:31:34,566
(Five years ago)
Really?

561
00:31:34,646 --> 00:31:35,447
Take a look.

562
00:31:36,606 --> 00:31:38,166
I hope you can use this notebook

563
00:31:38,166 --> 00:31:40,527
to record the wonderful life
you'll have after this.

564
00:31:41,007 --> 00:31:42,086
Thank you, Yuci.

565
00:31:44,637 --> 00:31:45,800
(To my best friend, Liangliang.
From Rao Yuci)

566
00:31:45,846 --> 00:31:47,287
You two are best friends indeed.

567
00:31:47,287 --> 00:31:48,806
It's like I have a second daughter now.

568
00:31:54,250 --> 00:31:55,000
(To my best friend, Liangliang.
From Rao Yuci)

569
00:31:55,100 --> 00:31:57,462
(Early Entrepreneurial Background
of Rao Shusheng, Father of Rao Yuci)

570
00:32:02,237 --> 00:32:03,890
(Harmonious relationship with wife,
strained relationship with Rao Yuci.)

571
00:32:03,891 --> 00:32:06,175
(Shanghai Bund Bank Deputy President Resigns
to Return Home to Support Husband's Business)

572
00:32:11,775 --> 00:32:12,950
(Trustworthy. Exploitable)

573
00:32:28,325 --> 00:32:30,337
(Gold Medal Honours in High School,
Key High School)

574
00:32:30,862 --> 00:32:34,187
(Loves Sweets.
Emotionally Available. Exploitable)

575
00:32:34,200 --> 00:32:35,366
I don't want to stay here for too long.

576
00:32:35,366 --> 00:32:36,350
I don't know him that well.

577
00:32:36,366 --> 00:32:37,967
You still dare to say that?
It's been four years, you know?

578
00:32:37,967 --> 00:32:39,270
Why do you still not know him well?

579
00:32:39,287 --> 00:32:40,487
Why did he invite me, then?

580
00:32:40,487 --> 00:32:41,687
How should I know?

581
00:32:42,846 --> 00:32:44,086
Is he trying to court you?

582
00:32:44,086 --> 00:32:44,927
If so, I'm not going.

583
00:32:44,967 --> 00:32:45,767
This won't do!

584
00:32:46,207 --> 00:32:47,806
Muran!

585
00:32:48,687 --> 00:32:49,487
Hurry up.

586
00:32:49,846 --> 00:32:50,646
Liangliang.

587
00:32:51,886 --> 00:32:52,806
Let me introduce her.

588
00:32:53,047 --> 00:32:54,886
This is my best friend, Rao Yuci.

589
00:32:55,967 --> 00:32:57,366
This is Bai Muran, our senior.

590
00:32:57,366 --> 00:32:58,566
He's in International Trade.

591
00:32:59,047 --> 00:32:59,886
Hello, Yuci.

592
00:33:01,080 --> 00:33:02,527
I wanted to get to know you long ago.

593
00:33:06,500 --> 00:33:13,562
(Loves Sweets. Emotionally Available.
Exploitable. Contact with Bai Muran)

594
00:33:15,487 --> 00:33:16,287
Muran.

595
00:33:16,687 --> 00:33:18,086
You should send Yuci back.

596
00:33:18,207 --> 00:33:19,126
I'll leave with you.

597
00:33:19,287 --> 00:33:20,806
We don't stay on the same road.

598
00:33:21,086 --> 00:33:22,166
Muran will send you home.

599
00:33:22,566 --> 00:33:23,967
His friend will send me home.

600
00:33:24,300 --> 00:33:25,890
Do you live at Four Seasons Condominium?

601
00:33:30,646 --> 00:33:32,527
I was there as well
during your thesis defense.

602
00:33:34,846 --> 00:33:36,846
You did such a great job.

603
00:33:38,086 --> 00:33:38,886
Thank you.

604
00:33:40,727 --> 00:33:41,527
Prodigy,

605
00:33:42,727 --> 00:33:44,366
there's one thing I wish to know.

606
00:33:44,487 --> 00:33:45,287
What is it?

607
00:33:48,326 --> 00:33:49,447
Do you have a boyfriend?

608
00:33:56,086 --> 00:33:58,086
What happened last night?

609
00:34:00,047 --> 00:34:00,846
He...

610
00:34:01,320 --> 00:34:03,125
He asked me
whether I had a boyfriend or not.

611
00:34:04,527 --> 00:34:05,625
Does that mean

612
00:34:05,846 --> 00:34:07,126
he wants to court you?

613
00:34:08,967 --> 00:34:09,847
I don't know.

614
00:34:10,086 --> 00:34:11,487
I was pretty surprised as well.

615
00:34:13,086 --> 00:34:14,407
What's so surprising about that?

616
00:34:14,407 --> 00:34:15,407
You're already graduating from college,

617
00:34:15,407 --> 00:34:16,407
yet you haven't been
in a relationship before.

618
00:34:16,407 --> 00:34:17,750
That's the most surprising thing.

619
00:34:17,967 --> 00:34:19,726
I think Bai Muran is pretty great.

620
00:34:19,726 --> 00:34:21,246
You can consider it.

621
00:34:23,407 --> 00:34:24,206
Fine, then.

622
00:34:25,967 --> 00:34:28,206
Once Chuxia gets another huge project,

623
00:34:28,766 --> 00:34:30,527
let's go on a trip together, okay?

624
00:34:31,766 --> 00:34:32,566
Okay.

625
00:34:33,126 --> 00:34:34,766
We can go anywhere you want.

626
00:34:42,975 --> 00:34:44,075
(To my best friend, Liangliang.
From Rao Yuci)

627
00:35:00,606 --> 00:35:01,407
Hello?

628
00:35:01,566 --> 00:35:02,646
Are you back?

629
00:35:03,327 --> 00:35:04,327
I'll arrive tomorrow.

630
00:35:06,246 --> 00:35:08,126
(Muran, I need you.)

631
00:35:14,050 --> 00:35:15,837
(Lysen Group)

632
00:35:15,887 --> 00:35:16,686
Hurry and look.

633
00:35:16,807 --> 00:35:17,606
This is

634
00:35:17,766 --> 00:35:19,407
the very first reform

635
00:35:19,407 --> 00:35:20,990
Mr. Jiang implemented
upon arriving at Lysen Group.

636
00:35:21,126 --> 00:35:22,847
It's a morning information
sharing session.

637
00:35:23,887 --> 00:35:25,246
Everyone involved in

638
00:35:25,327 --> 00:35:26,887
market investment analysis

639
00:35:26,887 --> 00:35:28,166
will come here.

640
00:35:28,566 --> 00:35:29,807
Everyone will exchange

641
00:35:29,807 --> 00:35:30,967
and share information here.

642
00:35:31,007 --> 00:35:32,246
And, they will decide together

643
00:35:32,246 --> 00:35:33,640
whether to retain a project or not.

644
00:35:33,847 --> 00:35:34,686
But you two?

645
00:35:36,327 --> 00:35:37,487
You two are quite lucky.

646
00:35:37,690 --> 00:35:39,980
Usually, we don't have the chance
to come to this place.

647
00:35:40,047 --> 00:35:40,847
Why is that?

648
00:35:42,367 --> 00:35:43,246
We specialize in

649
00:35:43,246 --> 00:35:44,967
fundamental project analysis.

650
00:35:46,527 --> 00:35:48,086
Our industry reports

651
00:35:48,086 --> 00:35:50,086
can only be used as their references.

652
00:35:52,686 --> 00:35:53,566
That's the person

653
00:35:53,566 --> 00:35:55,007
with real power to decide
the company's life or death.

654
00:35:55,166 --> 00:35:56,527
(Lysen Group Investment Dept 2, Chen Xi)
Meet Chen Xi,

655
00:35:57,086 --> 00:35:57,887
the vice president of Investment Dept 2.

656
00:36:01,847 --> 00:36:03,206
If so, why did they tell us

657
00:36:03,206 --> 00:36:04,447
to join the session today?

658
00:36:04,447 --> 00:36:05,447
Great job.

659
00:36:06,967 --> 00:36:07,766
Everyone,

660
00:36:08,166 --> 00:36:10,447
the morning information sharing session
will begin soon.

661
00:36:12,327 --> 00:36:13,166
Listen,

662
00:36:13,166 --> 00:36:15,126
you guys'd better behave today.

663
00:36:15,407 --> 00:36:16,206
Rao Yuci!

664
00:36:22,962 --> 00:36:26,530
=Episode 4=
(The Oriole)

665
00:36:27,140 --> 00:36:29,580
(All animals in this production
were treated humanely)

666
00:36:29,580 --> 00:36:35,780
♪Take a breath and swallow
the words you couldn't say♪

667
00:36:36,540 --> 00:36:39,740
♪No need to force your heart anymore♪

668
00:36:39,740 --> 00:36:44,260
♪Searching for the season
we once missed♪

669
00:36:44,260 --> 00:36:51,780
♪Leave this place,
though wounded still stay strong♪

670
00:36:51,780 --> 00:36:55,700
♪You must believe
one day the rain will fall♪

671
00:36:55,700 --> 00:36:59,740
♪And wash away the mud
that stains your soul♪

672
00:36:59,740 --> 00:37:03,260
♪Find your freedom in the wild♪

673
00:37:03,260 --> 00:37:07,220
♪Take your stride and move ahead♪

674
00:37:07,220 --> 00:37:11,380
♪I will stay behind
and wait for your eyes♪

675
00:37:11,380 --> 00:37:15,580
♪To rebuild
the same flesh and soul again♪

676
00:37:15,580 --> 00:37:19,380
♪Wander freely through the thorns♪

677
00:37:19,380 --> 00:37:23,460
♪Keep walking through the light♪

678
00:37:23,460 --> 00:37:27,660
♪Fate is absurd, don't stop for anyone♪

679
00:37:27,660 --> 00:37:33,980
♪What you dare to lose
will one day be your own♪

680
00:37:51,100 --> 00:37:57,740
♪I'm sorry, I still owe you these words♪

681
00:37:57,740 --> 00:38:01,580
♪An apology that came too late♪

682
00:38:01,580 --> 00:38:06,220
♪Yet it's also the path
that saves my soul♪

683
00:38:06,300 --> 00:38:13,700
♪When the cold wind
passes it takes the past away♪

684
00:38:13,700 --> 00:38:17,780
♪You must believe and stand unwavering♪

685
00:38:17,780 --> 00:38:21,860
♪There will be hands
to pull you from the deep♪

686
00:38:21,860 --> 00:38:25,860
♪Find your freedom in the silence♪

687
00:38:25,860 --> 00:38:29,620
♪Let your wounds be mended♪

688
00:38:29,620 --> 00:38:33,820
♪Gray is not the past
and pain is not a shame♪

689
00:38:33,820 --> 00:38:37,980
♪Sometimes the sunlight
makes the world look crueler♪

690
00:38:37,980 --> 00:38:41,700
♪Wander through the echoes of regret♪

691
00:38:41,700 --> 00:38:45,740
♪Be forgiven and be sheltered♪

692
00:38:45,740 --> 00:38:49,780
♪After everything shatters,
hold my hand♪

693
00:38:49,780 --> 00:38:55,980
♪A flower reborn
will finally bloom forever♪
